/*
 * Snippet for Module 4: Trackpad + Encoder
 * Components: Trackpad (I2C), Encoder
 * Pin Mapping:
 *   - Trackpad: I2C (D4/D5) + INT (D7)
 *   - Encoder A: D0
 *   - Encoder B: D1
 */

/*
